---
title: Caribbean Pork Chickpeas & Veggie Pie with Potato Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing plant-based pie! A coconutty, Caribbean-spiced chickpea filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/671b1b528ad42be8e34601c6-abf766e4.jpeg
